      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "Lower-latency OpenMP-style minimalistic scoped thread-pool designed for 'Fork-Join' parallelism in Rust and C++, avoiding memory allocations, mutexes, CAS-primitives, and false-sharing on the hot path \ud83c\udf74"
    },
